<view class="scroll-page">
  <view class="scroll-hero">
    <view class="scroll-kicker">炼制案台</view>
    <view class="scroll-title">火候未定</view>
    <view class="scroll-subtitle">此处分卷暂记材料与炉火脉络，后续将承载真正的炼制法门。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="section-title">案前记述</view>
    <view class="status-note">
      当前版本尚未开放完整炼制流程，但会以此页承接未来的配方、材料与成器结果。
    </view>
    <view wx:if="{{run}}" class="detail-grid">
      <view class="detail-cell">
        <text class="detail-label">现存灵石</text>
        <text class="detail-value">{{run.resources.spirit_stone}}</text>
      </view>
      <view class="detail-cell">
        <text class="detail-label">待用药草</text>
        <text class="detail-value">{{run.resources.herbs}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
